{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10108747555104-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10108747555104-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100123911791-1","P_10100123911791-2","P_10100123911791-3","P_10100123911791-4","P_10100123911791-5","P_10100123911791-6","P_10100123911791-7","P_10100123911791-8","P_10100123911791-9"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":420,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><strong>启示</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">这是发生在童年的一件小事。我的爸爸或许已经把它忘了，然而，这件事却对我的一生有着莫大的影响。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">那年我九岁。一日，我坐在靠门边的桌前写大字。门铃响了，爸爸开门，是邻居。两人就站在大门外交谈。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">那天风很猛，把我的大楷本子吹得“啪啪”作响，我拿着墨汁淋漓的笔去关门，猛地把门一推，然而，大门由于碰到障碍物反弹回来；与此同时，我听到父亲尽力压抑但仍然压不下去的喊叫声。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">门外的父亲，眉眼嘴唇，全都痛得扭成一团，好像连头发也痛得一根一根地站了起来，而他的十根手指呢，怪异地缠来扭去。</span>一看到我伸出门外一探究竟的脸，父亲即刻暴怒地扬起了手，想打我的耳光，但是，不知怎的，手掌还没有盖到我的脸上来，便颓（tuí）然放下，我的脸颊，仅仅感受到一阵风而已。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">邻居以责怪的口气对我说道：“你太不小心了，你父亲的手刚才扶在门框上，你看也不看，就把门用力关上……”啊！原来我几乎把爸爸的手指夹断！</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">我偷眼瞧父亲，他铁青着脸搓着手指，没有看我。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">十指连心，父亲此刻剧烈的痛楚，我当然知道，但是，当时的我毕竟只是一个九岁的儿童，我所关心的、所害怕的，是父亲到底会不会再扬手打我。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">当天晚上，父亲五根手指肿得很大，母亲在厨房里为他涂抹药油。我无意中听到父亲对母亲说道：“我实在痛得极惨，原想狠狠打他一个耳光，但是，转念一想，我是自己把手放在夹缝处的，错误在我，凭什么打他！”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">父亲的几句话，给了我毕生受用的无穷的启示。谢谢您，爸爸！</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"文中画线的句子，让你体会到父亲（　）。","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"正忍受着手指被门夹的剧烈疼痛。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"因忍耐着对我的怒火。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"题目“启示”的含义是（　）。","answers":[{"answer":"2","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"做父母的不要随便打自己的孩子。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"做事要细心，粗心是要惹祸的。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"自己犯了错，要敢于承认。不可迁怒他人，推卸责任。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCov